I would like to present: 

Ka_Arcane
=========

Being undiscovered for centuries, a group of scientists studying an area in the mountainous region discovered an ancient sanctuary located deep inside the mountain. Unfortunately for them, this discovery comes with a agonising hefty price. 

A 7 vs 7 map, the battle take place totally indoors with some amazing scenery and lightning containing ported CSGO and custom models by jimonions.
Not to mention that this map has fully working ambient and soundscape! Some texture were also custom made by hhh316 of Deviantart, make sure to check his cool stuff!
Enjoy! 

If you found anything unusual, please inform me.
--------------------------------------------------------

This map is part of < MG_Arcane > 
Which is planned to be released in January/February 2014!

--------------------------------------------------------

Credits:
